'''Football Manager Classic 2015''' ('''FMC2015''') is a game by [[Sports Interactive]]. It is improved from [[Football Manager Handheld]] (FMH). It has [[2D graphics|2D]] and [[3D graphics]]. It is similar to the classic mode of [[Football Manager]].

==Gameplay==
It contains 51 Nations and 117 Leagues. It was released on April 8.<!-- what year? -->  It is for only Android and IOS.  It has many changes from FMH.<ref>(http://www.footballmanager.com/content/football-manager-classic-2015)</ref>

