This article is a list of professional '''world champions''' in the '''[[Pool (cue sports)|pocket billiards]] (pool) [[cue sport]]''' known as '''[[eight-ball]]''', and its variations.
==World Standardized Rules ("American-style") eight-ball== This section lists world champions in the internationally standardized game of [[eight-ball]], as played by professionals around the world. This is played, like in [[nine-ball]], on the American 9-foot [[Billiard table|pool tables]] with coloured, numbered balls.
